292
00:18:05,780 --> 00:18:06,490
Hurry.

293
00:18:06,850 --> 00:18:08,190
I'm going upstairs, then.

294
00:18:08,190 --> 00:18:08,560
Go ahead.

295
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:09,700
Get to sleep early.

296
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:10,080
Don't...

297
00:18:11,010 --> 00:18:11,840
Got it.

298
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:13,310
Hurry. Go back to your room.

299
00:18:13,310 --> 00:18:14,180
Here I go.

300
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:14,740
Good night.

301
00:18:14,740 --> 00:18:15,190
Good night.

302
00:18:17,540 --> 00:18:18,570
Don't play with your phone.

303
00:18:18,570 --> 00:18:19,490
Stop. Leave them there.

304
00:18:19,490 --> 00:18:20,050
I'll carry them for you.

305
00:18:20,390 --> 00:18:21,340
I'll take the small one up.

306
00:18:21,340 --> 00:18:21,820
Okay.

307
00:18:26,970 --> 00:18:28,420
That was close.

308
00:18:43,610 --> 00:18:44,570
Hello, Ms. Zhang.

309
00:18:44,850 --> 00:18:45,870
How much would you like to pay?

310
00:18:46,610 --> 00:18:47,680
35,000?

311
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:49,680
Fine. I'll put it down.

312
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:51,040
Remember to transfer the money to me soon.

313
00:18:51,460 --> 00:18:52,430
Okay. Bye.

314
00:18:53,230 --> 00:18:53,860
He,

315
00:18:54,010 --> 00:18:54,630
you'll buy some?

316
00:18:54,630 --> 00:18:55,250
20,000?

317
00:18:55,250 --> 00:18:56,490
Mr. Ding. Ms. Liu.

318
00:18:56,490 --> 00:18:57,390
15,000?

319
00:18:57,390 --> 00:18:58,300
50,000?

320
00:18:58,300 --> 00:18:59,360
Okay. Okay.

321
00:19:01,910 --> 00:19:03,330
Look, look.

322
00:19:03,980 --> 00:19:05,880
The family counts on me.

323
00:19:06,280 --> 00:19:10,520
[Electricity bill, WeChat,
Ant Credit Pay, Bank card]

324
00:19:16,290 --> 00:19:17,920
I gave the money to mom.

325
00:19:18,460 --> 00:19:21,200
I have to make more money.

326
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:25,650
I can't wait until my money is used up.

327
00:20:04,220 --> 00:20:06,420
Please take care of Bei Duofen.

328
00:20:06,820 --> 00:20:08,140
I've written the tips about cats

