Here.

336
00:21:10,790 --> 00:21:11,680
What's this?

337
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:14,690
Pickles. I made them.

338
00:21:15,410 --> 00:21:15,960
How is it?

339
00:21:27,280 --> 00:21:29,520
[Recruitment for management trainees, waitresses,
apprentice cooks, bar attendants, and part-time posts]

340
00:21:32,690 --> 00:21:33,530
Hello.

341
00:21:33,530 --> 00:21:35,360
Welcome. How many of you?

342
00:21:35,360 --> 00:21:36,670
I'm not here for lunch.

343
00:21:36,670 --> 00:21:38,050
I came to find a job.

344
00:21:38,710 --> 00:21:39,940
Get in to see the boss.

345
00:21:40,580 --> 00:21:41,710
Okay. Thank you.

346
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:49,200
Hello, boss.

347
00:21:49,540 --> 00:21:51,540
I saw your recruitment.

348
00:21:51,540 --> 00:21:53,160
I want to ask about the details.

349
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:54,270
What should a part-time worker do?

350
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:57,670
Come and help

351
00:21:57,670 --> 00:21:59,800
at mealtimes.

352
00:22:12,780 --> 00:22:15,730
Just like you,

353
00:22:15,890 --> 00:22:19,300
the house is lack of human touch.

354
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:33,940
Isn't it great?

355
00:22:34,530 --> 00:22:35,650
Don't worry.

356
00:22:35,650 --> 00:22:37,220
When I move out,

357
00:22:37,220 --> 00:22:38,990
I'll restore it to its former look.

358
00:22:47,650 --> 00:22:51,350
Not even the succulent plants?

359
00:22:51,590 --> 00:22:53,780
I'll keep them in my room.

360
00:22:53,780 --> 00:22:55,520
They don't take up much space.

361
00:23:37,410 --> 00:23:39,330
So rich of you.

362
00:23:39,330 --> 00:23:41,060
Don't flaunt wealth like this.

363
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:51,090
Let's call it a day.

364
00:23:54,260 --> 00:23:56,000
By the way, Ms. Bei,

365
00:23:56,190 --> 00:23:57,820
why didn't I see you

366
00:23:58,010 --> 00:23:59,080
in the last episode of that show?

367
00:24:00,790 --> 00:24:02,830
Something unexpected happened

368
00:24:02,830 --> 00:24:04,020
and I quit in advance.

369
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:08,430
I had planned to cheer for you.

370
00:24:09,810 --> 00:24:10,610
It's okay.

371
00:24:10,610 --> 00:24:12,360
I've never thought about
my love life, anyway.

372
00:24:13,220 --> 00:24:14,200
Think about it, then.

373
00:24:17,910 --> 00:24:19,130
In the best years of your life,

374
00:24:19,940 --> 00:24:22,730
what a waste if you don't enjoy the romance!

375
00:24:23,240 --> 00:24:24,770
It'll be a real waste

376
00:24:24,770 --> 00:24:26,700
if I don't pursue my dream
in the best years of my life.

377
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:33,600
Why...

378
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,050
Why are your ears so red?

379
00:24:37,570 --> 00:24:38,640
Is anyone cursing you?

380
00:24:43,150 --> 00:24:44,140
Watch your language.

381
00:24:45,210 --> 00:24:46,910
We don't know why,

382
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:48,640
but his show was canceled.

383
00:24:50,780 --> 00:24:51,890
Don't make an improper remark.

384
00:25:16,760 --> 00:25:17,140
Hello.

385
00:25:17,580 --> 00:25:18,740
Hello, Uncle.

386
00:25:19,200 --> 00:25:20,200
Tang Li is leaving hospital today.

387
00:25:20,410 --> 00:25:21,850
I plan to invite her and Erduo

388
00:25:21,850 --> 00:25:23,040
to dinner for celebration.

389
00:25:23,040 --> 00:25:23,940
Would you like to join us?

390
00:25:23,940 --> 00:25:25,010
Are you available?

391
00:25:28,320 --> 00:25:29,410
Let me check my schedule.

392
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:37,020
I'm available. When?

393
00:25:37,870 --> 00:25:39,900
Today. Where would you like to go?

394
00:25:41,140 --> 00:25:42,610
A restaurant we once visited

395
00:25:42,610 --> 00:25:43,470
or a new restaurant?

396
00:25:46,770 --> 00:25:48,080
Food in restaurants isn't healthy.

397
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,220
It's greasy, too.

398
00:25:50,220 --> 00:25:51,210
When Tang Li is just out of the hospital,

399
00:25:51,540 --> 00:25:52,570
she should have a light diet.

400
00:25:54,110 --> 00:25:55,090
It's thoughtful of you.

401
00:25:55,510 --> 00:25:56,560
Where shall we have dinner, then?

402
00:25:59,370 --> 00:26:00,170
At home.

403
00:26:00,610 --> 00:26:02,780
Home? Who will cook?

404
00:26:03,530 --> 00:26:04,400
I can't even

405
00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:05,760
boil the water very well.

406
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:09,000
Tang Li is out of the hospital,
but she can't cook.

407
00:26:09,540 --> 00:26:10,070
Erduo...

408
00:26:11,010 --> 00:26:13,190
I'm not sure if she can cook.

409
00:26:14,650 --> 00:26:15,410
You have me.

410
00:26:16,110 --> 00:26:16,570
You?

411
00:26:17,220 --> 00:26:19,930
But Uncle, I've never seen you
cook Chinese dishes.

412
00:26:20,850 --> 00:26:23,440
Will you make us order takeout food?

413
00:26:24,610 --> 00:26:25,310
Rest assured.

414
00:26:25,850 --> 00:26:26,770
I'll cook.

415
00:26:27,360 --> 00:26:28,660
All you need to do is invite them.

416
00:26:30,080 --> 00:26:30,530
Okay.

417
00:26:33,970 --> 00:26:35,000
Let's have dinner at my home.

418
00:26:35,380 --> 00:26:36,180
I count on you.

419
00:26:42,910 --> 00:26:45,560
I can finally leave hospital.

420
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:48,890
I'm so bored.

421
00:26:50,580 --> 00:26:52,900
Congratulations on your leaving hospital.

422
00:26:53,620 --> 00:26:55,660
Let me check how you have recovered.

423
00:26:56,360 --> 00:26:57,500
I've fully recovered.

424
00:26:57,730 --> 00:26:58,430
Look, look.

425
00:26:59,940 --> 00:27:01,810
When I lay in bed, I got fatter.

426
00:27:02,040 --> 00:27:03,150
I could have left hospital a long time ago.

427
00:27:04,410 --> 00:27:05,990
You still need more rest.

428
00:27:06,210 --> 00:27:06,870
Got it.

429
00:27:06,870 --> 00:27:08,140
The discharge procedures are done.

430
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,680
Come on.

431
00:27:15,360 --> 00:27:17,080
Why are you not careful
even when you're in hospital?

432
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:18,740
Who do you think you are, Wonder Woman?

433
00:27:20,790 --> 00:27:21,700
What do I do, then?

434
00:27:22,050 --> 00:27:23,900
Boss Yu, will you give me more days off

435
00:27:24,180 --> 00:27:25,710
so that I can travel around the world?

436
00:27:25,710 --> 00:27:26,600
No. No.

437
00:27:27,220 --> 00:27:28,240
Miss Tang.

438
00:27:28,770 --> 00:27:29,880
Director Tang.

439
00:27:30,630 --> 00:27:31,880
Why are you still angry?

440
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:34,900
What can I be angry at?

441
00:27:36,020 --> 00:27:37,070
You're the boss, anyway.

442
00:27:51,380 --> 00:27:53,080
I'll go get the car.

443
00:27:53,380 --> 00:27:55,130
Check if anything is left behind.

444
00:27:55,690 --> 00:27:57,180
Let's meet at the gate
of the In-patient Department.

445
00:28:00,560 --> 00:28:01,150
Wait, Mr. Yu.

446
00:28:05,130 --> 00:28:05,920
Thank you.

447
00:28:08,730 --> 00:28:09,500
You're welcome.

448
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:15,350
I'll get packed.

449
00:28:19,340 --> 00:28:26,060
[In-patient Department]

450
00:28:26,060 --> 00:28:29,300
[No. 1 People's Hospital]

451
00:28:46,010 --> 00:28:46,770
Come on. Get in the car.

452
00:29:15,780 --> 00:29:17,230
Shall we go have dinner

453
00:29:17,700 --> 00:29:19,030
in celebration of Li's leaving hospital?

454
00:29:19,030 --> 00:29:19,800
Good idea.

455
00:29:20,450 --> 00:29:21,920
It's good news.

456
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:23,130
We must celebrate it.

457
00:29:23,360 --> 00:29:24,130
Yeah.

458
00:29:24,130 --> 00:29:25,090
I've got everything arranged.

459
00:29:25,760 --> 00:29:26,800
When she's just out of the hospital,

460
00:29:26,800 --> 00:29:28,940
she must have a light diet.

461
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:29,820
Let's have dinner at my home.

462
00:29:32,620 --> 00:29:34,270
Mr. Yu, you can cook?

463
00:29:34,270 --> 00:29:37,010
No. I can't cook.

464
00:29:37,010 --> 00:29:38,840
But I've got a strong helper.

465
00:29:39,990 --> 00:29:41,460
Helper?

466
00:29:41,660 --> 00:29:43,210
Yeah. My uncle, I mean.

467
00:29:43,210 --> 00:29:44,320
He cooks perfectly.

468
00:29:45,430 --> 00:29:47,650
You asked your uncle to cook for us?

469
00:29:47,650 --> 00:29:48,870
Is it appropriate?

470
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:53,790
Actually, my uncle is

471
00:29:54,520 --> 00:29:55,600
Ye Shuwei.

472
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:00,560
It's no big deal.

473
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:02,420
I'm two years older than him.

474
00:30:02,860 --> 00:30:04,430
When I grew up, I kept following him

475
00:30:04,430 --> 00:30:06,040
and calling him Uncle.

476
00:30:06,310 --> 00:30:08,160
It's quite shameful.

477
00:30:08,670 --> 00:30:10,000
So, in front of strangers,

478
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:11,150
I usually call him Guru Ye.

479
00:30:11,390 --> 00:30:12,990
But you're not strangers.

480
00:30:12,990 --> 00:30:14,020
It's okay to let you know.

481
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:16,480
I knew it.

482
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:17,760
I wondered why Ye Shuwei

483
00:30:17,760 --> 00:30:20,190
participated in such a show for you.

484
00:30:48,390 --> 00:30:50,660
Ma'am, how much is this?

485
00:30:50,980 --> 00:30:51,810
Young man,

486
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,860
it's been a long time
since you came last time.

487
00:30:57,870 --> 00:30:58,490
Oh, it's you?

488
00:31:00,620 --> 00:31:02,310
Hasn't your girlfriend come with you?

489
00:31:03,300 --> 00:31:03,910
She...

490
00:31:05,630 --> 00:31:06,530
She's too busy.

491
00:31:07,790 --> 00:31:08,410
Oh, I see.

492
00:31:08,940 --> 00:31:11,360
So, you do the grocery shopping and cook?

493
00:31:12,760 --> 00:31:15,910
A man isn't charming unless he can cook.

494
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:19,590
Roses or chocolate

495
00:31:20,020 --> 00:31:21,680
can't be as good

496
00:31:21,840 --> 00:31:24,340
as a delicious meal for your girl.

497
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:25,410
That's right.

498
00:31:26,050 --> 00:31:27,440
Here. The mushrooms are good.

499
00:31:27,990 --> 00:31:29,140
Very fresh. Come on.

500
00:31:34,040 --> 00:31:34,710
Almost enough.

501
00:31:35,190 --> 00:31:35,850
Pack them, please.

502
00:31:35,850 --> 00:31:36,610
Okay. Okay.

503
00:31:36,610 --> 00:31:37,150
Thank you.

504
00:31:42,590 --> 00:31:43,860
Okay. 14.5 yuan.

505
00:31:46,630 --> 00:31:47,030
Here.

506
00:31:49,210 --> 00:31:49,710
Thank you.

507
00:32:05,950 --> 00:32:08,770
Li is tired after all this. Let her sleep.

508
00:32:09,910 --> 00:32:10,900
You go take a rest, too.

509
00:32:11,410 --> 00:32:12,270
Ye Shuwei has arrived.

510
00:32:12,710 --> 00:32:13,670
When he's around,

511
00:32:13,670 --> 00:32:15,520
all we need to do is sit and wait.

512
00:32:17,860 --> 00:32:18,630
Sit and wait?

513
00:32:20,850 --> 00:32:22,150
Is it appropriate?

514
00:32:23,150 --> 00:32:24,470
I'd like to go and see

515
00:32:24,470 --> 00:32:26,450
if I can help him with anything.

516
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:36,410
How can I help you?

517
00:32:38,940 --> 00:32:39,550
Wash the vegetables.

518
00:32:42,540 --> 00:32:43,090
This?

519
00:33:05,390 --> 00:33:06,740
Why will you throw them away?

520
00:33:06,740 --> 00:33:08,290
They'll taste great after they're pickled.

521
00:33:08,290 --> 00:33:09,480
Li just left hospital.

522
00:33:09,480 --> 00:33:10,720
Pickles with porridge will be great for her.

523
00:33:38,510 --> 00:33:39,000
What?

524
00:33:41,230 --> 00:33:41,990
Where did you get this?

525
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:44,100
It's a secret.

526
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:45,760
Come over. Let me do it.

527
00:33:50,330 --> 00:33:52,180
Could you lower your head?
I can't reach your hair.

528
00:34:00,970 --> 00:34:01,490
Done.

529
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:02,460
Cool.

530
00:34:07,540 --> 00:34:08,160
Thank you.

531
00:34:11,810 --> 00:34:12,670
You're welcome.

532
00:34:26,410 --> 00:34:27,470
Awesome.

533
00:34:27,910 --> 00:34:30,340
I didn't expect you to make western meals

534
00:34:30,340 --> 00:34:31,810
as well as Chinese meals.

535
00:34:33,100 --> 00:34:33,810
Am I awesome?

536
00:34:34,680 --> 00:34:35,260
Yes.

537
00:34:36,180 --> 00:34:38,920
Most of the men can only boil

538
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:42,020
frozen dumplings or instant noodles.

539
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:43,120
For example,

540
00:34:45,860 --> 00:34:46,400
Mr. Yu.

541
00:34:47,450 --> 00:34:49,460
Everyone can cook unless he's disabled.

542
00:34:49,850 --> 00:34:52,120
When he doesn't cook, he's just lazy.

543
00:34:53,770 --> 00:34:55,640
Don't bet on it, you know.

544
00:34:55,640 --> 00:34:57,820
Some people love cooking,

545
00:34:57,820 --> 00:34:59,270
but they can't cook very well.

546
00:34:59,270 --> 00:35:00,080
My mother, for example.

547
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:08,230
Come on. Taste it.

548
00:35:26,050 --> 00:35:27,970
You don't like Chinese dishes, do you?

549
00:35:29,520 --> 00:35:30,770
It doesn't mean I can't make them.

550
00:35:42,600 --> 00:35:43,330
Wipe it.

551
00:35:44,220 --> 00:35:45,060
The stain is on your sweatshirt.

552
00:36:04,220 --> 00:36:04,840
Are you all right?

553
00:36:05,380 --> 00:36:06,530
I'm all right.

554
00:36:07,040 --> 00:36:07,740
It's okay.

555
00:36:08,630 --> 00:36:09,410
Why is your face

556
00:36:10,420 --> 00:36:11,410
burning like mad?

557
00:36:15,910 --> 00:36:17,320
I guess I'm hot

558
00:36:17,830 --> 00:36:20,940
because of the poor ventilation.

559
00:36:22,090 --> 00:36:23,230
I feel so hot.

560
00:36:26,260 --> 00:36:26,980
You may leave the kitchen.

561
00:36:27,500 --> 00:36:28,370
I can handle it alone.

562
00:36:30,010 --> 00:36:31,400
You don't need my help?

563
00:36:31,970 --> 00:36:32,480
No.

564
00:36:33,750 --> 00:36:35,360
When you're here, you only distract me.

565
00:36:35,970 --> 00:36:37,830
I'll get the dish to the table.

566
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:45,100
Mr. Yu, be seated.

567
00:36:45,100 --> 00:36:46,750
I called Li. She'll be out soon.

568
00:36:47,620 --> 00:36:48,530
Come on, Li.

569
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:53,960
What a big dinner!

570
00:36:54,390 --> 00:36:56,370
But why are they all your favorite dishes?

571
00:36:58,430 --> 00:36:59,560
Thank you for your hard work.

572
00:37:01,270 --> 00:37:02,840
Ye Shuwei made the dishes.

573
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:03,690
